{
  "stem": "10588.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And when they brought us in in the ghetto, who lived with us?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They brought us a family whose name was Wiatrak.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Wiatrak.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know when a mill where they make-- goes around like-- the wind blows to make it to-- when you try to mill corn and wheat.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I forgot.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know what it's called in English.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But their family name was Wiatrak, because I remember.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So well, previously--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Wiatrak is W-I-A-T-R-A-K, Wiatrak.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So where previously was one family, but six or seven families was put in one apartment.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they didn't have any modern facilities either.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So you can imagine what was going on there when this one wanted to go to the store, this one was the facilities to use-- it was extremely, extremely hard.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Another thing-- you know, so many things you remember later-- is that when we were-- before we came, they made, you know, a Jewish-- they took Jewish policemen.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Jewish-- it was like in the ghettos, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They had Jewish self-government it was almost called.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But they were supposed to do what the Nazis told them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But anyhow, so we moved into this house, to this--",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Before we went to the ghetto?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not really, because first of all, we did it in hiding to the extent that we can, you know.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we couldn't make Passover anymore.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What would you make it?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You didn't have any food.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We were watched.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It wasn't-- but we still tried to observe the rituals as far as we can, you know, as far as we could.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Still kept on saying the [YIDDISH] and all the things.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the [YIDDISH] the little piece.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But we couldn't go on anymore.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It no longer was-- the last Passover that I celebrated with my family was in Passover 1939.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
